snippet.title: Can My Mimic Defeat Margit NG+? - Elden Ring Patch 1.04 (Strength Build)
snippet.description:
We test a 10+ mimic that's using the strength build that's been changed a slight bit, all I know of for now is that the swing speed is quicker. Other than that this is the best strength build I know of for now. Greatswords have been altered a bit but I would rather go for double giant crusher instead. "Seems to do more damage."

NG+ Mimic VS NG+ Margit...
